EASTERN MEDITERRANEAN SEA.
STRAIT OF SICILY.
TUNISIA.
DNC 08, DNC 09.
1. DUE TO SAFETY MEASURES TO COMBAT COVID-19,
   ALL TUNISIAN PORTS WILL BE CLOSED TO
   PLEASURE CRAFT, FISHING VESSELS AND
   PASSENGER SHIPS UNTIL FURTHER NOTICE.
2. CONTACT TUNISIAN COAST GUARD AND LOCAL PORT
   AUTHORITIES FOR FURTHER INSTRUCTIONS.
3. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1014/20.
